<h2 id="jump-link-who-is-performing-at-the-2026-super-bowl">Who is performing at the 2026 Super Bowl halftime show?</h2> 
<p>Bad Bunny, who holds the title as the most-streamed artist in the world, will be headlining the 2026 Super Bowl halftime performance. You can expect that show to begin after the second quarter, likely between 8-8:30 p.m. ET. Singer Charlie Puth will also be at the game to perform the National Anthem, Brandi Carlile is scheduled to sing "America The Beautiful," and Coco Jones will perform "Lift Every Voice and Sing."</p> 
