('How to buy a GPU in 2026', 'https://www.engadget.com/gaming/pc/how-to-buy-a-gpu-160100017.html?src=rss', '<p>One of the toughest parts of any new computer build or upgrade is finding the right video card. In a gaming PC, the GPU is easily the most important part, and you can limit your experience by going with the wrong model. The buying process can be frustrating, especially right now with <a href="https://www.engadget.com/computing/crucial-is-a-casualty-of-ais-hunger-for-ram-185910113.html">memory shortages</a> leading to higher prices. In this guide, we''ll help you navigate the market and find the right GPU for your needs.</p>
